# Terms of Use
Medical Disclaimer
This app is for information purpose only. Nothing in the app, Ultimate 531, is meant as medical advice. Suggestions that may have worked for others, may not work for you. Lifting weights has risks of injury and you might get injured at some point. Consult with your doctor before trying anything within the app.

